snippet.title: Powerslide for 3DO Gameplay demo
snippet.description:
This is a video demo of the stand-alone and gameplay of the upcoming 3DO title POWERSLIDE.

You may notice there is no sound, thats because there is none in the game. I merged several of the level demos together to show you what tracks are actually available on the game should they be enabled someday.

Sadly, all thats really playable at the moment are the street & sand rally levels. Still not bad.
